UID:a1b205f6b8ec5d1d@earlyon-cal
DTSTAMP:20260621T102747Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260615T133000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260615T153000
SUMMARY:Baby and Me (birth to 12 months)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:You and your baby are invited to join us for songs\, rhymes\, a
 nd experiences designed to help you connect with your baby. Enjoy engaging
  conversations and information sharing on healthy child development. It's 
 a great way to connect with your baby\, other families and educators.\n\n*
 *Please bring indoor shoes for the program room (or non-slip grippy socks 
 for baby).**\n\n*Note: Program will include active learning experiences th
 at help develop your child's gross motor skills.*\n\nDrop-in\n\nCentre: Ea
 rlyON Markham Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/
 earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:08f3879b59288abb@earlyon-cal
DTSTAMP:20260621T102747Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260615T133000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260615T153000
SUMMARY:Let's Talk (birth to 6 years old)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the opportunity to speak with educators and other f
 amilies. Topics may include child development\, available community inform
 ation\, newcomer and pre- and postnatal supports. Community partners may a
 lso join to offer their expertise.\n\n**Let’s Talk with FoodShare: Baby 
 Food Presentation (for parents/caregivers of children 0-12 months\, or for
  expecting parents)**\n\nThis session focuses on introducing solid foods t
 o babies aged 0 to 12 months. Participants will learn:\n* When and how to 
 introduce solid foods\n* What types of foods to start with\n* How much to 
 feed\n* Why it’s important to begin with certain foods\n\nPre-registrati
 on required\n\nCentre: EarlyON Markham Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missi
 oninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
