DTSTAMP:20260621T102747Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260616T091500
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260616T111500
SUMMARY:Exploring STEAM (12 months to 6 years old)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:This program invites you and your child(ren) to explore STEAM (
 science\, technology\, engineering\, art\, and math) ideas. Children will 
 investigate\, play\, communicate\, and experiment\, making learning a fun 
 and interactive experience. Join us to discover the exciting world of STEA
 M and watch your child’s curiosity and creativity grow! It’s a great w
 ay to connect with other families and educators.\n\n**Please bring indoor 
 shoes for the program room.**\n\nDrop-in\n\nCentre: EarlyON Markham Centre
 \n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
