LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:This program invites you and your child(ren) to engage in singi
 ng\, rhyming\, and storytelling! This program supports development of lang
 uage and literacy skills in a fun and engaging way. It’s a great way to 
 connect with other families and educators.\n\n**This is a pre-registered V
 IRTUAL program in CANTONESE (please attend all 4 sessions). Zoom link will
  be provided in advance of the program.**\n\n*NOTE: If you pre-register AF
 TER June 5\, please email earlyonmarkham@familydaycare.com to let us know\
 , so we may send you the link to join.*\n\nPre-registration required\, Vir
 tual\n\nCentre: EarlyON Markham Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.c
 om/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
