DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260616T153000
SUMMARY:Parent-Child Mother Goose Program® (birth to 12 months)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:This program invites you and your baby or young child to a grou
 p experience that focuses on the pleasure and power of using rhymes\, song
 s\, and stories together. You will be introduced to skills that can enhanc
 e your confidence to create positive family patterns during your child's c
 ritical early years. Everyone can benefit from enjoyable\, healthy experie
 nces with language and communication. It’s a great way to connect with o
 ther families and educators.\n\n**This is a pre-registered program for Bir
 th to 12 months (please attend all 7 sessions). Please bring indoor shoes 
 for the program room.**\n\nPre-registration required\n\nCentre: EarlyON Ma
 rkham Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/
 calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
