SUMMARY:Ready\, Set\, Move (12 months to 6 years old)
LOCATION:7755 Bayview Avenue\, Thornhill\, ON L3T 4P1
DESCRIPTION:This program invites you and your child(ren) to join us and get
  moving together! “Ready\, Set\, Move!” is packed with experiences to 
